entries.femaleVariant: Barely made it back with the transport yesterday.
Heh, just be glad you didn't show up empty-handed. Jumped me twice already. All I delivered was an empty truck.
Ya think that's bad. Turns out my exhaust pipe was so twisted, it's a miracle I'm still breathing.
Goddamn mechanic gave me some old Aldecaldo junk again. And I paid like it was brand spankin' new.
Ugh, mechanics... always takin' you for a ride. First on parts, then on the back of a tow truck.
